## FeatureModifierId enum

Feature Modifier ids to choose which OmvFeatureModifer should be used in OmvDecoder.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export declare enum FeatureModifierId 
```

## Enumeration Members

|  Member | Value | Description |
|  --- | --- | --- |
|  default | <code>0</code> | Generic feature modifier used when no other modifiers are defined. You do not need to specify it in \[\[OmvDataSourceParameters\]\] as it is added by default if no other feature modifier is used. |
|  tomTom | <code>1</code> | Identifier to use the OmvTomTomFeatureModifier in the OmvDecoder. |
